data.text:
Glenn proposed with an engagement ring which cost $40,000 at Jean Danker's parents place. He has two marriages behind him, one to ex-radio DJ Kate Reyes, and then to TV host Jamie Yeo.

Hope this marriage lasts... married so many times already.
